    <p class="about-p r d2" data-en>Intensive Practice (집중수도) is a concentrated retreat program under the direct guidance of the Grandmaster. Running as 1-night 2-day retreats and regular sessions, participants deepen their practice through dharma talks, Life Field training, and Seongmyeol elevation.</p>
    <blockquote class="blockq r d2" data-ko>
      "수도자 1인은 세상자 만인이요,<br>중생자 억이라"<br>
      <small style="font-size:.8em;opacity:.7">— 큰스승님 말씀 (대구 우리조 강의)</small>
    </blockquote>
    <blockquote class="blockq r d2" data-en>
      "One practitioner equals ten thousand in the world,<br>and a billion in the realm of liberation."<br>
